tions of scientists are introduced to biodiversity studies.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Dunnum, Jonathan L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Cook, Joseph A.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/6af5eb3c44123738599667fe02bc0428", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/4d4c22b2e1f2130c06b6b56eeff7f985a0cf634b36e73070260f41903f77ed23", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/ZISZ7WCI", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/ZISZ7WCI", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/79f9720cbef03298074181f8c9f051e6!/b41763-44229", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "4", "title": "mammalia", "volume": "76"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/6af5eb3c44123738599667fe02bc0428"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:ZISZ7WCI"}, {"identifier": "10.1515/mammalia-2012-0071"}], "communities": [{"id": "biosyslit"}, {"id": "batlit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "13480143"}}]}}, "title": "Gerrit Smith Miller: his influence on the enduring legacy of natural history collections", "links": {"self": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/13480144", "self_html